                            <comment id="12990886" author="daijy" created="Sat, 5 Feb 2011 02:44:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem happens when we have nested UDF:&lt;br/&gt;
1. Inner UDF does not define complete outputSchema&lt;br/&gt;
